casebody.data:
The HUNTINGTON NATIONAL BANK, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Thomas CULLEN, Mrs. Thomas Cullen, His Wife, Felice Cullen, Mr. Cullen Husband of Felice Cullen, Defendants-Petitioners. C-845 September Term 2017
080551 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005461-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
